{"tid":1935051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美澳科學家：武漢肺炎病毒 SARS-CoV-2 自然演化而成","createTime":"2020-03-20T09:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T11:47:31.000Z","uid":55851,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b48c519371b932074e01eaa4ccda73fe9dc962","tid":1935051,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/xi-04_P9gh4_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fxi-04_P9gh4_1200x0.png&h=6ad4b4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 爆發，坊間已有不少陰謀論指病毒是由人工製作。最新刊於《自然醫學》的研究指出，引發武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 的 SARS CoV 2 不是人為製造或改造而成。<br />\n<br />\n報告指， SARS CoV 2 是已知第 7 種會感染人類的冠狀病毒，且與 MERS Cov 及 SARS CoV 一樣會影響嚴重病症，其餘 4 種冠狀病毒包括 HKU1 ､ NL63 ､ OC43 及 229E 等都與輕微症狀相關。美國及澳洲生物學家團隊利用基因組數據對比分析 (comparative analysis of genomic data) ，嘗試找出病毒源頭。<br />\n<br />\n雖然病毒刺突狀蛋白與人體受體 ACE2 結合能力極高，但分析顯示該蛋白與受體的相互作用並不理想，而且也與沙士的基因序列不同。團隊認為，要人工製造病毒，是以已知病毒為藍本製作病毒。然而，此病毒和其蛋白與已知病毒不同。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他們也指 SARS CoV 2 的病毒受體結合區 (receptor binding domain, RBD) 與穿山甲相似，因此有理由相信病毒是經自然演化而成。團隊又估計，病毒最初宿主是蝙蝠，並可能由兩個情景演化至今： 1) 由動物跳躍至人類前已演變出致病性，或是 2) 在感染人類後，在人類細胞才演化出致病性。<br />\n<br />\n此外，研究人員也發現病毒的刺突狀蛋白之間的功能性多鹼基切割位點 (polybasic cleavage site)。他們估計該切割位點有機會是在人類之間演變而成，而這切割位點亦與一種禽流感病毒株相似，令其傳染性增加。研究人員之一的 Kristen Andersen 指：「這兩個病毒特性，即其刺狀蛋白受體結合區 (RBD) ，以及其獨特結構的發現，均排除了病毒是人工改造而成的結果。」<br />\n<br />\n研究人員之一的生物學家 Andrew Rambaut 提醒，現時未知道病毒是否在跳躍至人類前已演變出其致病性。假設病毒早已出現致病性，則代表此病毒株仍然在動物中流行，有機會在未來再次跳躍至人類間爆發。 <br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\nScienceDaily, COVID-19 coronavirus epidemic has a natural origin, 17 March 2020<br />\n<br />\n報告：<br />\nAndersen, K.G., Rambaut, A., Lipkin, W.I. &amp; et al. (2020). The proximal origin of SARS-CoV-2. Nat Med (2020). doi: 10.1038/s41591-020-0820-9<br />\n<br />\n文／Edward Ho 、審核／Alan Chiu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E6%BE%B3%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-sars-cov-2-%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%BC%94%E5%8C%96%E8%80%8C%E6%88%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-sars-cov-2-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2584%25B6%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%258C%2596%25E8%2580%258C%25E6%2588%2590%2F&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=5927856f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-sars-cov-2-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2584%25B6%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%258C%2596%25E8%2580%258C%25E6%2588%2590%2F&h=22bc0722\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E6%BE%B3%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-sars-cov-2-%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%BC%94%E5%8C%96%E8%80%8C%E6%88%90/</a>"},{"pid":"489c3c394a24dd7464a23f2124875395cc1fa0db","tid":1935051,"uid":68689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/us-04_u1uGj_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fus-04_u1uGj_1200x0.png&h=5ab9ce69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"845fd4f4ba3bafab48e50f141fa3b933fd5192f9","tid":1935051,"uid":82450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"美國投毒夢碎"},{"pid":"d32900212dbb55d0997ba9a6e26aad1bd4d70dcd","tid":1935051,"uid":15098